{"tid":716082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係琴日西貢搭1A既粗心男","createTime":"2018-06-25T03:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T03:54:34.000Z","uid":192165,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"51b76d106375c5685dceffced256ce8f8f69544b","tid":716082,"uid":192165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>    是咁的，話說琴日跟FD去左西貢一個島仔度玩。 個個島仔度我撞到個同屋企人一齊去既女仔，望住佢睇風景既樣，果陣就好想識佢，但鼓唔起勇氣去搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n    <span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>離開西貢大約五點幾，好巧合咁係回程小巴度坐佢後面個位，直到落車個陣，我睇唔到佢漏左頂帽係個位度，急急腳就衝左落地鐵站，之後我個FD講返，還返頂帽比佢。<br />\n    <span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>到返屋企果陣，落左場好大既雨，衝返屋企個陣諗返呢件事，決定開出我第一個post。我好後悔琴日唔夠細心，把握唔到呢個巧合去識佢，但都唔祈望佢會認得我，只係想記錄低呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有沒巴打可以安慰下我"},{"pid":"766a6ef2c0bf62ecc562470bca054cd860e40ef8","tid":716082,"uid":105051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"人地有仔架啦"},{"pid":"379468c51394103661dbb0584977ecab02acb871","tid":716082,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"好撚毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee2dede2213415b21b6859f12be9bbd2c3d463d","tid":716082,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"死毒撚"},{"pid":"4c982c039f8cec7c3f8847726be073919068919c","tid":716082,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6cb72977edda59e4faa7db6892b866c2262882","tid":716082,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":